jnxUtil.name: jnxUtil
jnxUtil.contactinfo: Juniper Technical Assistance Center Juniper Networks, Inc. 1194 N. Mathilda Avenue Sunnyvale, CA 94089 E-mail: support@juniper.net
jnxUtil.description: This MIB module provides a generic means for exposing junos data via SNMP. There are separate tables for each type of data, and specific instances of each type are identified by its corresponding name.

jnxUtilCounter32Table.name: jnxUtilCounter32Table
jnxUtilCounter32Table.description: This table exposes generic Counter valued objects. Each counter instance, which can be populated via an internal junos interface, is identified by its corresponding name.

jnxUtilCounter32Entry.name: jnxUtilCounter32Entry
jnxUtilCounter32Entry.description: Each entry exposes a separate Counter instance.

jnxUtilCounter32Name.name: jnxUtilCounter32Name
jnxUtilCounter32Name.description: The name assigned to this Counter instance.

jnxUtilCounter32Value.name: jnxUtilCounter32Value
jnxUtilCounter32Value.description: The value of this generic, utility counter instance.

jnxUtilCounter32Time.name: jnxUtilCounter32Time
jnxUtilCounter32Time.description: The time at which this instance was last populated.
